OL,3,CEducation Minister ignored official
OL,4,Cadvice when he agreed to meet the LCC
OL,6,FUTV can reveal that the Education
OL,7,FMinister Paul Givan ignored the advice
OL,8,Fof officials in his department when he
OL,9,Fagreed to meet the Loyalist
OL,10,FCommunities Council at Parliament
OL,11,FBuildings in September.
OL,13,FDocuments just released to UTV, also
OL,14,Fshow that while the Minister met the
OL,15,FLCC six months after the initial
OL,16,Fmeeting request was made, he had
OL,17,Fagreed to it within weeks.
