OL,3,CEducation Minister ignored official
OL,4,Cadvice when he agreed to meet the LCC
OL,6,FThe Education Minister Paul Givan and
OL,7,Fhis DUP party colleague Communities
OL,8,FMinister Gordon Lyons both faced heavy
OL,9,Fcriticism from other political parties
OL,10,Ffor agreeing to meet the Chairman of
OL,11,Fthe LCC David Campbell and other
OL,12,Frepresentatives from the group.
OL,14,FThe Loyalist Communities Council
OL,15,Frepresents Loyalist paramilitary
OL,16,Fgroups including the UDA and UVF, and
OL,17,Fwas set up in 2015. It says it is
OL,18,Fcommitted to helping the groups they
OL,19,Frepresent transition away from
OL,20,Fviolence and crime.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/9
