OL,3,CEducation Minister ignored official
OL,4,Cadvice when he agreed to meet the LCC
OL,6,FHowever, within days of the initial
OL,7,Frequest from the Chairman of the LCC
OL,8,Fto meet the Education Minister Paul
OL,9,FGivan, an official drew up a 'Quick
OL,10,FAdvice' document for the Minister.
OL,12,FIn it, the official wrote, 'It is
OL,13,Frecommended that you should decline
OL,14,Fthe invitation'.
OL,16,FThe official then cites, 'It is not
OL,17,Fentirely clear what specific issues Mr
OL,18,FCampbell would wish to discuss' as the
OL,19,Freason for declining the meeting.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/9
