OL,3,CEducation Minister ignored official
OL,4,Cadvice when he agreed to meet the LCC
OL,6,FThe person who gave the advice works
OL,7,Fin the Department of Education's
OL,8,FTackling Educational Disadvantage Team.
OL,10,FThe Chairman of the LCC David Campbell
OL,11,Ftold UTV last month, he first
OL,12,Frequested the meetings with the
OL,13,Fministers on the 1st March 2024, just
OL,14,Fweeks after they took up office on the
OL,15,Freturn to Stormont.
OL,17,FThe documents released to UTV through
OL,18,Fa freedom of information request show
OL,19,Fthat by the 4th March officials were
OL,20,Falready discussing whether the meeting
OL,21,Fshould take place.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/9
