OL,6,FThe meeting between the Education
OL,7,FMinister Paul Givan and
OL,8,Frepresentatives of the Loyalist
OL,9,FCommunities Council took place on the
OL,10,F24th September at Parliament Buildings.
OL,12,FMinutes of the meeting, also seen by
OL,13,FUTV, are very short.
OL,15,FThe one A4 side page lists those who
OL,16,Fattended the meeting as the Minister,
OL,17,Fhis special advisor and private
OL,18,Fsecretary.
