OL,6,FIt also lists those representing the
OL,7,FLoyalist Communities Council - its
OL,8,Fchairman David Campbell, Robert
OL,9,FWilliamson, Bobby Rodgers and Jackie
OL,10,FMcDonald.
OL,12,FIt lists in a short paragraph the
OL,13,Fmatters discussed. They included
OL,14,Feducational underachievement in north
OL,15,Fand west Belfast; absenteeism in
OL,16,Fschools post-Covid; the RAISE
OL,17,Fprogramme; the Fair Start report;
OL,18,FEarly Years interventions; the Bright
OL,19,FSpark programme; the Labour Party
OL,20,Fmanifesto commitment to provide a
OL,21,Fmental health worker for every school.
